premise_source_doc_sentence: Amarkalam  (  First Class  )  is a 1999 Tamil romantic musical-action film written and directed by Saran and produced by V. Sudhir Kumar for the banner Venkateswaralayam .
The film featured Ajith Kumar , making it his 25th film and Shalini in the lead roles with Raghuvaran , Raadhika and Nassar in other pivotal roles .
The film opened in August 1999 to positive reviews from critics and became a blockbuster .
